<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="title">用户界面</view>
    <view class="subtitle">先填写并保存你的用户信息，然后查看与你相关的订单通知和结果。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="service-banner status-{{serviceState}}">
    {{serviceMessage}}
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">用户信息</view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">用户 ID</text>
      <input class="input" value="{{receiverId}}" bindinput="handleInput" />
      <view class="field-help">联调默认收货人 ID 已预填，保存后会自动轮询通知。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="field switch-row">
      <text class="field-label" style="margin-bottom: 0;">只看未读</text>
      <switch checked="{{unreadOnly}}" bindchange="toggleUnreadOnly" />
    </view>
    <view class="field-help" style="margin-top: -6rpx; margin-bottom: 18rpx;">
      开启后，列表里只显示还没有标记为已读的通知。
    </view>

    <view class="button-row">
      <button class="ghost-btn" bindtap="saveReceiver">保存信息</button>
      <button class="primary-btn" loading="{{loading}}" bindtap="fetchNotifications">刷新通知</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">通知列表</view>
    <view class="section-caption">这里展示与你相关的送达、失败和取消通知，点击可进入订单详情。</view>
    <block wx:if="{{loadError}}">
      <view class="empty">{{loadError}}</view>
    </block>
    <block wx:elif="{{!receiverId}}">
      <view class="empty">请先填写并保存用户 ID，再查看与你相关的通知。</view>
    </block>
    <block wx:elif="{{loading && !notifications.length}}">
      <view class="empty">正在加载通知列表...</view>
    </block>
    <block wx:elif="{{notifications.length}}">
      <block wx:for="{{notifications}}" wx:key="id">
        <view class="list-item">
          <view class="item-title">{{item.title}}</view>
          <view class="item-subtitle">{{item.content}}</view>
          <view class="item-meta">订单：{{item.order_id}} | 类型：{{item.type_text}}</view>
          <view class="button-row" style="margin-top: 14rpx;">
            <button class="ghost-btn" size="mini" data-order-id="{{item.order_id}}" bindtap="openOrder">查看订单</button>
            <button wx:if="{{!item.read_flag}}" class="primary-btn" size="mini" data-notification-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="markRead">标记已读</button>
          </view>
        </view>
      </block>
    </block>
    <view wx:else class="empty">暂无通知，等配送状态变化后会在这里显示结果。</view>
  </view>
  <view class="page-footnote">
    <view>全国大学生嵌入式芯片与系统设计竞赛</view>
    <view class="page-footnote-team">地线引力队</view>
  </view>
</view>
